# <type>[optional scope]: <description>
#
# [optional body]
#
# [optional footer(s)]
#
# Types:
#   feat     (new feature for the user, not a new feature for build script)
#   fix      (bug fix for the user, not a fix to a build script)
#   docs     (changes to the documentation)
#   style    (formatting, missing semi colons, etc; no production code change)
#   refactor (refactoring production code, eg. renaming a variable)
#   test     (adding missing tests, refactoring tests; no production code change)
#   chore    (updating grunt tasks etc; no production code change)
#
# Examples:
#   feat: add support for custom encryption algorithms
#   fix: resolve issue with password validation
#   docs: update README with new usage examples
#   style: format code according to style guide
#   refactor: extract encryption logic into separate service
#   test: add unit tests for ProjectService
#   chore: update dependencies
#
# Breaking changes:
#   feat!: change default encryption method
#
#   BREAKING CHANGE: The default encryption method has changed from AES-128 to AES-256-GCM.
